  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of a mailed educational brochure on
      adherence to referral for screening colonoscopy. The comparison (or control) group receives
      no mailer, which is usual care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
